cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for style transfer, which are typically covered in the arXiv sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses adversarial generation techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper evaluates the technique on sentiment, gender, and political slant, which are all topics that fall under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
